---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Botox for Hyperhidrosis | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'Medical use of botulinum toxin type A to reduce excessive underarm sweating when topicals are ineffective. Onset in ~2–4 days with relief that can last months.',
  canonical: '/services/botox-for-hyperhidrosis/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'Botox for Hyperhidrosis (Axillary)',
      serviceType: 'Botulinum toxin intradermal treatment',
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      },
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/botox-for-hyperhidrosis/'
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Injectables</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Botox for Hyperhidrosis</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        Targeted intradermal injections to reduce excessive underarm sweating when topical options fall short.
        Subtle, functional relief with minimal downtime.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Onset</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">~2–4 days</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Typical Duration</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">4–12 months</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Technique</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Intradermal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Minimal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">

      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Primary hyperhidrosis causes excessive focal sweating—often in the underarms—beyond what’s needed
            for temperature control. When antiperspirants or topical therapies are ineffective or poorly tolerated,
            botulinum toxin type A can be used to temporarily reduce sweat by blocking acetylcholine release to
            the sweat glands in the treated area.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Benefits at a glance</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Significant sweat reduction in the treated zone
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Onset commonly within 2–4 days; measurable at follow-up
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Relief that can last several months (often 4–12)
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Outpatient, minimally invasive, no incisions
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Precision matters. We map the highest-activity zones and use small intradermal injections
            at evenly spaced points for a balanced, effective result.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Evaluation & mapping</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Confirm candidacy and rule out secondary causes.</li>
                <li>Identify high-sweat areas (may include starch-iodine mapping).</li>
                <li>Outline a tailored treatment plan and follow-up.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">The treatment</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Intradermal micro-injections placed in a small grid.</li>
                <li>Multiple points per underarm for even coverage.</li>
                <li>Visits are typically brief; discomfort is usually mild.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 sm:col-span-2">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Timeline</div>
              <div class="mt-2 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm text-neutral-700">
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-3">
                  <div class="font-medium">24–48 hrs</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-neutral-600">Early reduction for many patients.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-3">
                  <div class="font-medium">~4 weeks</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-neutral-600">Clinical assessment of response.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-3">
                  <div class="font-medium">Months</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-neutral-600">Gradual return; retreat when needed.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Aftercare</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Avoid rubbing, massaging, or heavy pressure on the area for 24 hours.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Skip high-intensity workouts for 24 hours.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Avoid harsh deodorants or perfumes immediately after treatment.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
              Mild redness, tenderness, or small bruises may occur and usually settle quickly.
              Contact the clinic if you experience unusual weakness, difficulty swallowing or breathing,
              or any unexpected symptoms.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & considerations</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Common, temporary effects</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Injection-site tenderness, redness, swelling</li>
              <li>Small bruises</li>
              <li>Tingling or mild local discomfort</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Precautions & contraindications</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Pregnancy or breastfeeding: not advised</li>
              <li>Active skin infection at the site</li>
              <li>Known allergy to botulinum toxin components</li>
              <li>Neuromuscular disorders: discuss risks with your provider</li>
              <li>Some areas (palms, soles, face) are higher-sensitivity and may be off-label</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Educational information only; not medical advice. Candidacy, dosing, and intervals are determined by your clinician.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">When will I start to sweat less?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Many notice improvement within 24–48 hours, with continued reduction over the next several days.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How long do results last?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Relief commonly lasts 4–12 months. Timing varies by individual and area treated; repeat when symptoms return.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Does it stop sweating everywhere?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              No—the effect is local to the treated area. Normal thermoregulation elsewhere is not blocked.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Is it painful?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Most describe mild pinching or stinging. Hands and feet can feel more sensitive than underarms.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Wondering if you’re a candidate? We’ll review your history and outline a conservative plan.
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
